.el .ds Aq '
.TH codemark 1  "codemark 0.4.1" 
.SH NAME
codemark \- A structural bookmarking system for code using tree\-sitter queries
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBcodemark\fR [\fB\-\-db\fR] [\fB\-\-format\fR] [\fB\-\-verbose\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fB\-V\fR|\fB\-\-version\fR] <\fIsubcommands\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
A structural bookmarking system for code using tree\-sitter queries
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-db\fR \fI<DB>\fR
Database location; repeatable for cross\-repo queries
.TP
\fB\-\-format\fR \fI<FORMAT>\fR
Output format: json (default), table, line, or tv (or a custom template)
.TP
\fB\-\-verbose\fR
Enable debug\-level logging to stderr
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Print version
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
codemark\-add(1)
Create a bookmark from a file and byte range
.TP
codemark\-add\-from\-snippet(1)
Create a bookmark by matching a code snippet from stdin against a file
.TP
codemark\-add\-from\-query(1)
Create a bookmark from a file and a raw tree\-sitter query
.TP
codemark\-resolve(1)
Resolve a bookmark to its current file location
.TP
codemark\-show(1)
Display full details of a bookmark
.TP
codemark\-remove(1)
Remove bookmarks by ID
.TP
codemark\-heal(1)
Heal bookmarks by resolving and updating their status
.TP
codemark\-status(1)
Print a summary of bookmark health
.TP
codemark\-list(1)
List bookmarks with optional filters
.TP
codemark\-preview(1)
Show the current location of a bookmark (file, line, byte range)
.TP
codemark\-search(1)
Full\-text search across notes and context
.TP
codemark\-reindex(1)
Rebuild semantic search embeddings for all bookmarks
.TP
codemark\-collection(1)
Manage named groups of bookmarks
.TP
codemark\-diff(1)
Show bookmarks affected by recent changes
.TP
codemark\-gc(1)
Remove old archived bookmarks
.TP
codemark\-export(1)
Export bookmarks to stdout
.TP
codemark\-import(1)
Import bookmarks from a JSON file
.TP
codemark\-completions(1)
Generate shell completions
.TP
codemark\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
.SH VERSION
v0.4.1
